OL,3,CCampbell likens Starmer to Bush as he
OL,4,Cwarns of 'dark place' if Labour fails
OL,6,FFormer Number 10 spin doctor Alastair
OL,7,FCampbell has warned the UK could end
OL,8,Fup in a "dark place" if the Labour-run
OL,9,FUK Government fails as he likened
OL,10,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,11,Fformer US president George W Bush.
OL,13,FSpeaking to Holyrood Magazine, the
OL,14,Fformer adviser to Sir Tony Blair said
OL,15,FSir Keir struggles to get his
OL,16,Fpersonality across in the media.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
