OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777269939
OL,3,CCampbell likens Starmer to Bush as he
OL,4,Cwarns of 'dark place' if Labour fails
OL,6,FFormer president Mr Bush gained a
OL,7,Freputation for gaffes during his time
OL,8,Fin the White House ` years where he
OL,9,Fspent a significant amount of time
OL,10,Fwith Sir Tony during his time in
OL,11,FDowning Street ` but Mr Campbell spoke
OL,12,Fhighly of him.
OL,14,F"He reminds me, to this regard only,
OL,15,Fof George W Bush," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
