OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777269939
OL,3,CCampbell likens Starmer to Bush as he
OL,4,Cwarns of 'dark place' if Labour fails
OL,6,F"Because if this government, if this
OL,7,FLabour government, doesn't succeed I
OL,8,Fthink we're going to a pretty dark
OL,9,Fplace."
OL,11,FMr Campbell did concede, however, the
OL,12,FGovernment's unpopularity had been a
OL,13,F"massive drag" on the Scottish Labour
OL,14,Fcampaign ahead of the May 7 election
OL,15,Fin Scotland, adding that he was
OL,16,F"really sad" for leader Anas Sarwar.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]uD@AOUuD@NO]xD@AOUxD@LO]
