OL,3,CCampbell likens Starmer to Bush as he
OL,4,Cwarns of 'dark place' if Labour fails
OL,6,FIn recent years, the party has gone
OL,7,Ffrom competing with the SNP to be the
OL,8,Flargest party to fighting it out with
OL,9,FReform for second place, according to
OL,10,Fthe polls, though senior Labour
OL,11,Ffigures remain confident Mr Sarwar
OL,12,Fcould end up in Bute House after May 7.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
